name: NERPM43 (JTA Model)
body:
### Welcome to NERPM43 (JTA Model) GitHub Pages.
This site maintains the NERPM43 model development and documentation. Since GitHub effectively allows multiple users to work in the same space and track changes much more efficiently, the development process is version tracked in GitHub. The entire model contents can be found here [NERPM 43 Model](https://github.com/4Step/NERPM43). Download the latest release from here and click the above link for all previous releases. For the list of issues please check [Issues Resolved](https://github.com/4Step/NERPM43/issues?utf8=%E2%9C%93&q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aclosed).

### Authors and Contributors
